Excited to work together!

[Your name]
```

**2. Get payment before starting**

Always. No exceptions. For new clients:
- 50% upfront for projects
- Full payment upfront for small jobs
- Weekly billing for ongoing work

**Payment tools (all free to receive):**
- PayPal
- Stripe
- Wise (for international)

---

